        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 21 at 5:26PM CDT by NWS Austin/San Antonio TX</headline>
        <description>At 526 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Hilltop, or near Dilley, moving north at 40 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts of 50 to 55 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Pearsall, Dilley, North Pearsall, Derby, Hilltop, Bluff, and Three
Oaks.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
